<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4673094>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6: Trichobothrial patterns of external aspect of pedipalp patella for genus Franckeus. Patterns based on specimen of F. peninsularis and, in part, on Sissom & Francke (1985: Figs. 11, 46) and Sissom (1991: Figs. 14, 34, 54). Orthobothriotaxy depicted as opened circles and accessory trichobothrium depicted as a closed circle." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4673094/files/figure.png" .

